{"tid":1153950,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城遭英格蘭足總指違反反禁藥條例，或有機會被褫奪今季英超冠軍","createTime":"2019-05-14T03:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T03:29:50.000Z","uid":60916,"like":11,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49a50f63be026e94e4be919e82b14861db48db86","tid":1153950,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/1716353-%E6%9B%BC%E5%9F%8E%E9%81%AD%E8%8B%B1%E6%A0%BC%E8%98%AD%E8%B6%B3%E7%B8%BD%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%8F%8D%E7%A6%81%E8%97%A5%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B/?fromG=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F1716353-%25E6%259B%25BC%25E5%259F%258E%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E8%2598%25AD%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%258F%258D%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%2F%3FfromG%3D1&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHTx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=0879cfb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/1716353-%E6%9B%BC%E5%9F%8E%E9%81%AD%E8%8B%B1%E6%A0%BC%E8%98%AD%E8%B6%B3%E7%B8%BD%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%8F%8D%E7%A6%81%E8%97%A5%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B/?fromG=1</a><br />\n<br />\n曼城被指無法向反禁藥人員提供有關球員在哪裡進行藥檢的資料，違反英格蘭足總反禁藥 條例第14d條款。根據條例，球會需要提供有關訓練及球員所在地的準確資料，以便球員隨時接受藥檢，但曼城無法確認會方提供資料的可靠性，球會需要在本月19日之前回應。否則有機會被足總褫奪今季的英超冠軍，由原來第2位的利物浦取代成為今季的英超冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/045016_573b3479cff56596c7fed91efe452648.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F045016_573b3479cff56596c7fed91efe452648.png&h=3ea5ffc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e650c158d2a51fad32b5e099b7ff88d59212f2a","tid":1153950,"uid":60916,"like":3,"dislike":1,"sco